text: Antonio Djakovic (born 8 October 2002) is a Swiss swimmer. He competed in the men's 400 metre freestyle at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Swimmers at the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Male freestyle swimmers
